{
  "texts": [
    "Prediction was made and for each observation, we individually determined the most important predictors by SHAP value.",
    "Based on the similarity of the important predictors, we clustered the employees to obtain the most important factors leading to exit.",
    "A visualization is also presented to evaluate clusters.",
    "Figure 1 represents the main steps of the proposed data-driven approach.",
    "In addition, the pseudo code is given in Code 1."
  ]
}